<h5>Are you looking for an amazing avatar generator for your website users? ruby_randimage is your gem!</h5>

<h5>A powerful, customizable and sophisticated awesome SVG avatars generator from several options such as symmetries, size, color palette and color densities.</h5>

<h5>RubyRandimage is a pure Ruby library without any dependencies.</h5>



<div class="jumbotron">
  <h3>Customize your icon!</h3>
  <p>Generate your awesome icons trying several options and click on generate</p>
  <%= render partial: 'demo/form' %>
  <div class="well well-sm">RubyRandimage.create(:title => title, :colors => colors, :symmetry_axes=> [axe_x, axe_y], :num_cells => cells)</div>


  <h3>Example1</h3>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-8">
      <div class="well well-sm">RubyRandimage.create(:title => title, :colors => colors, :symmetry_axes=> [axe_x, axe_y], :num_cells => cells)</div>

      <%= submit_tag 'Generate' %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-4">
    </div>
    
  </div>


</div>


